        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Doolandella property values are driven by estate presentation quality, block usability and proximity to Forest Lake's retail hub. The suburb competes directly with Ellen Grove and Richlands for the same buyer, so condition and accurate pricing matter more here than in tighter inner-city markets.</p>
      </details>

