        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Doolandella is a quiet residential suburb with easy access to Forest Lake's shopping and leisure amenity, Centenary Motorway connections to the CBD, and the outdoor amenity of Forest Lake itself. It suits families who want modern estate living at an accessible price point in Brisbane's western corridor.</p>
      </details>

